ComicInfo.Title: The People-Breeders!; When Speaks the Dragon!
ComicInfo.Summary:
The People-Breeders!: Thor returns to earth and finds Jane Foster at the High Evolutionary's Wundagore.
When Speaks the Dragon!: Thor and companions inspect Nastrond for Odin. Volstagg wanders off and finds Fafnir.
